➜36氪创投陪伴计划 | 复星锐正资本：植根中国、布局全球、兼具产业平台和独立基金优势的顶尖投资机构
http://www.sohu.com/a/411994064_114778	35768
<p>复星锐正资本成立于2013年，总部位于北京，是复星集团旗下植根中国、布局全球、兼具产业平台和独立基金优势的顶尖投资机构。</p>
<p>目前，复星锐正的管理资产总规模达数十亿人民币。作为全球化的风险投资平台之一，复星锐正致力于在全球主要经济增长区域投资优秀的高成长、高科技企业，并已在中国、美国、印度、以色列等地设有7个办公室，打造出领先、有影响力的创业创新生态。</p>
<p>复星锐正始终坚持科技引领、持续创新，将全球动力嫁接全球资源。投资阶段覆盖初创期、成长期、成熟期至二级市场，投资规模从上百万美元到上亿美元不等，重点关注和全球家庭客户息息相关的互联网/移动互联网、金融、教育、消费零售、文化娱乐、汽车，以及技术驱动的未来科技、大数据、人工智能等众多领域。</p>
<p>未来，复星锐正将继续与全球创业者为伴，充分发挥投资的先导性作用，赋能优质产业资源；同时，紧抓全球经济转型带来的新动力和新机遇，协同被投企业快速布局全球市场，践行价值投资，与优秀的创业者相互赋能、共享成长！<span></span></p>
<p>Fosun RZ Capital was founded in 2013 and headquartered in Beijing. As an affiliate of Fosun Group, RZ Capital is an independent fund with strategic resources, quickly establishing global footprints.</p>
<p>Fosun RZ Capital has billions of RMB AUM. As one of the most globalized venture capital platforms in China, RZ Capital is committed to investing in high-growth, high-tech companies in major economic growth regions and has fostered innovation ecosystems around the world, with 7 offices in China, United States, India and Israel.</p>
<p>Fosun RZ Capital focuses on investing in science and technology innovation, and connecting global momentum to global resources. The investment stages include the seed stage, growth stage, late stage to the secondary market. The investment scale ranges from one to hundreds of millions of dollars. RZ Capital has a wide coverage on industries, including Internet / mobile Internet, finance, education, consumer retail, cultural and entertainment, automotive, and high technologies (big data, artificial intelligence) and many other fields that are closely related to global family customers.</p>
<p>Fosun RZ Capital will continue to partner with global entrepreneurs and provide global resources. Also, to grasp the new momentum and new opportunities brought by the global economic transformation, coordinate with the portfolio companies to quickly enter the global market, empower and grow with outstanding entrepreneurs.<span></span><span></span></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
